          "activation_name": "Unexpected Armament",
          "effect": "You reach into one of the coat\u2019s pockets and withdraw a chunk of metal that instantly expands into a common simple or martial melee weapon of your choice. The weapon functions as a *+1 striking weapon*. When you produce the weapon, you decide if it is made from cold iron or silver, and which one of the following property runes it gains: corrosive, flaming, frost, shock, or thundering. This weapon remains for 1 hour or until it leaves your grasp, at which point it vanishes.",
